; Regression test for issue #815: numeric_cast guards against overflow casts
;
; Verify that large integer values work correctly without silent overflow
; when converted through the expression engine.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $1000000
    Assets:Cash

; Verify that large integer arithmetic works correctly in expressions.
; The value 2147483647 is INT_MAX; values near it should be handled
; without silent truncation when used in integer contexts.
test bal --limit "amount > 0" --format "%(quantity(display_total))\n"
1000000
end test
